  <sec>
    <title>4 Conclusion</title>
    <p>We presented a mixture model framework and network inference algorithms to analyze sample-taxa matrices that are associated with <italic>K</italic> microbial networks. Future work will include the development of Bayesian approaches for model selection for this problem.</p>
    <p><italic>Conflict of Interest</italic>: none declared.</p>
